So basically you have your salad bowl in front of you.  You’ll need one large bowl to start.  Tossing a salad is a kind of art, so it’s kind of fun.  

So to start, here’s the first thing you’ll need to do.  You need to layer the salad ingredients in the bowl.  That’s the bottom of the salad!  Here’s a representation of that:

\begin{array}{ccc}
 \text{\Large Lettuce}
 & \text{\Large Carrots} & \text{\Large Celery} \\
 \text{\Large Cucumber}
 & \text{\Large Avocado} & \text{\Large Nuts} \\
 \text{\Large Tomatoes}
\end{array}
